Package: kdepimlibs5
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, kdepimlibs-data (>= ${source:Version}), libsasl2-modules
Replaces: akonadi-kde (<< 4:4.1.80), libkholidays4 (<< 4:4.2.90)
Conflicts: libkholidays4 (<< 4:4.2.90)
Description: core libraries for KDE PIM 4 applications
 This package contains Personal Information Management libraries needed to run
 KDE 4 applications.
 .
 This package is part of the KDE 4 PIM libraries module.

Package: kdepimlibs-data
Section: libs
Architecture: all
Replaces: libkholidays4 (<< 4:4.2.90)
Description: core shared data for KDE PIM 4 applications
 This package contains architecture-independent Personal Information Management
 data files needed to run KDE 4 applications.
 .
 This package is part of the KDE 4 PIM libraries module.

Package: kdepimlibs5-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: kdepimlibs5 (= ${binary:Version}), ${sameVersionDep:kdelibs5-dev},
Replaces: kdepimlibs-data (<< 4:4.1.80)
Conflicts: libkleopatra1-dev
Description: development files for the KDE 4 PIM libraries
 This package contains development files for building software that uses
 the KDE 4 Personal Information Management libraries.

Package: kdepimlibs-dbg
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Priority: extra
Depends: kdepimlibs5 (= ${binary:Version}), kdelibs5-dbg, libc6-dbg [amd64]
Description: debugging symbols for the KDE 4 PIM libraries
 This package contains debugging files used to investigate problems with
 binaries included in the KDE 4 PIM libraries module.
